edu.usm.sosw.sword.db

Interface CounselorDAO


  • public interface CounselorDAO
    This interface exists to provide proper access to the counselors table. SQL is written in the SqlUpdate and SqlQuery annotations above every function and then rewritten and executed by JDBI. The CounselorDAO interface is used by the CounselorResources class in the resources package. RegisterMapper annotation allows JDBI to bind the CounselorMapper class to this interface. Without the RegisterMapper annotation, the SQL query results would not bind properly to the Counselor Object.
    Version:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Sean T. Purvis
    See Also:
    Counselor, CounselorMapper, CounselorResource
